  "text": "The initial model used for RMC was based on a model determined from PDFgui but expanded to multiple unit cells. The basis of the model was the best fit of the 300 K neutron data with a reduced set of parameters (Table 3) , using only isotropic ADPs for compatibility with the RMC modelling program used, DISCUS (Proffen & Neder, 1997; [CITATION_1] . The data were fitted using PDFgui out to a large r range of up to 80 Å , as this provided the best starting model, although the RMC modelling was only refined out to 20 Å . The focus of the RMC fitting was on the 300 K neutron data as this was the highest quality data collected.",
